sectionText: If you get a 'course full' error message and want to be added to a wait list for this class, go to www.fshn.illinois.edu and click on Current Students then Waitlist Information.  DO NOT E-MAIL THE INSTRUCTOR FOR SPECIAL CONSIDERATION BEYOND THE WAITLIST POLICY.  Please just put yourself on the waitlist when it opens one week before classes start.  There is nothing further that can/will be done.
